{"word":"Birthright","slug":"birthright","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Birthright</b> Belonged to the firstborn<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=16'>Deu 21:16</a><br/> Entitled the firstborn to a double portion of inheritance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=17'>Deu 21:17</a><br/> Entitled the firstborn to royal succession<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=3'>2Ch 21:3</a><br/> An honorable title<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=22'>Exo 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=89&verse=27'>Psa 89:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=31&verse=9'>Jer 31:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=29'>Rom 8:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=1&verse=15'>Col 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=1&verse=6'>Heb 1:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=23'>Heb 12:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=5'>Rev 1:5</a><br/> Sold by Esau<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=34'>Gen 25:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=36'>Gen 27:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=16'>Heb 12:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=9&verse=13'>Rom 9:13</a><br/> Forfeited by Reuben<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=2'>1Ch 5:2</a><br/> Set aside, that of:<br/> - Manasseh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=48&verse=20'>Gen 48:20</a> <br/> - Adonijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=15'>1Ki 2:15</a> <br/> - Hosah's son<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book